header.title: Purple Sheep
header.info: A very active sheep with cute purple horns.[br][br]Par plays sounds, has many of the original animations, has plenty of custom animations, and lots of uncommon/rare/super rare animations![br][br]1.0 Changes:[br]New turning animation.[br]New bathing animations.[br]New whimpering sound.[br]Pump, the King Sheep, does flips,[br]spawns sheep, and disappears![br][br]Thanks for using![br]Basedon Green Sheep by Oliver B.[br]You can send feedback to[br]probello@gmail.com[br][br]Thank you, Paul R[br]- Oliver[br][br]Mar. 05, 2021.
